Bundestag Report States ESM May Be Unconstitutional, Bild Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-14T09:09:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/bundestag-report-states-esm-may-be-unconstitutional-bild-says.html
The European Stability Mechanism may
contravene the German constitution’s ‘debt-brake’ clause,
according to a document prepared for a parliamentarian who is a
member of  Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s party,  Bild newspaper  said,
citing a confidential document.  The report, written for Christian Democrat lawmaker Norbert
Brackmann, said that a “maximum drawdown” of the fund could
cost Germany “hundreds of billions” of euros, Bild reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
